import React, {useState} from 'react'; import axios from 'axios' function App() { const [data,setData]= useState({}) const [location,setLocation] =useState('') const url =`https://api.openweathermap.org/data/2.5/weather?q=${location}&appid=da8c1040837628e95a1ddbad0d86a369` const searchLocation = (event)=>{ if(event.key === 'Enter'){ axios.get(url).then((response)=>{ setData(response.data) console.log(response.data) }) setLocation('') } } return (
setLocation(event.target.value)} onKeyPress={searchLocation} placeholder="please enter the city" type="text"/>
